FBIS4-23742 "drafr115_a_94007" FBIS-AFR-94-115 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Cease-Fire Reached, Broken Almost Immediately Cease-Fire Reached, Broken Almost Immediately New UN Envoy Appointed EA1406170794 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in English to Rwanda 1100 GMT 14 Jun 94 EA1406170794 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura English BFN [Excerpts] The UN secretary general Butrus Butrus-Ghali has replaced his special representative to Rwanda, Dr. Jacques-Roger Booh-Booh. He is to be replaced by (Mohamed Khan) from Pakistan. [passage omitted] The man to replace Dr. Jacques-Roger Booh-Booh as the new UN secretary general special representative to Rwanda, (Mohamed Khan), has pledged to be impartial and transparent.
